<reference id="blackberry_io_sandbox" xml:lang="en-us">
    <title><apiname>sandbox</apiname></title>
    <shortdesc><i>Whether the file system is sandboxed. It is set to true by default.</i></shortdesc>
    <refbody>
    	<section>
    		<p>When sandbox is set to false, you must use absolute path to reference a file or directory, you can use <xref href="blackberry_io_sharedFolder.xml" scope="local">sharedFolder</xref>, <xref href="blackberry_io_home.xml" scope="local">home</xref> or <xref href="blackberry_io_SDCard.xml" scope="local">SDCard</xref> to construct file paths.</p>
    	</section>
        <section>
            <title>Synopsis:</title>
            <pre scale="80">Boolean blackberr.io.sandbox = true</pre>
        </section>
    </refbody>
</reference>
